These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, water, lemonade
City: liverpool, hamburg, colone, marseilles
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | lemonade | water | coffee | milk   |
| City   | hamburg  | liverpool     | colone   | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, asparagus, zucchini, garlic
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person eating garlic is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | zucchini | garlic | asparagus | lettuce    |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | backgammon      | monopoly | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, swimming, skateboarding
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, go
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | weightlifting | skateboarding | swimming   | handball |
| Game   | backgammon   | whist | go | scrabble         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, lettuce, banana, grapefruit
House: victorian, art-deco, palace, farmhouse
1. the art-deco house is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the palace house##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the victorian house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | grapefruit | lettuce | zucchini  | banana      |
| House         | art-deco | farmhouse   | palace | victorian |

