.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, baccarat, ritmeester, alhambra
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, polish, thai
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the polish is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the thai##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | ritmeester | baccarat | cain |
| Nationality    | australian       | thai | polish | pakistani     |

