.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
City: edinburgh, new-york, berlin, prague
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| City   | prague | berlin | edinburgh | new-york |
| Beverage           | sprite      | milk | mirinda | hot-chocolate    |

