.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, vegafina, oliveros, tiparillo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, daffodil, azalea
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Cigar   | oliveros | vegafina | bongani | tiparillo  |
| Flower           | daffodil | lily | azalea       | rose |

