.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, lilac, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, sudoku, photography
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Color         | lilac | lavender      | ebony | apricot |
| Hobby   | camping          | drawing | sudoku     | photography    |

