.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, soy-milk, juice
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cauliflower, blueberry, cabbage
1. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | soy-milk       | fanta | juice   |
| Food     | cauliflower | blueberry | cabbage   | cherry |

