.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, begonia, daffodil
House: cape-cod, modern, gothic-revival, farmhouse
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Flower    | rose | begonia  | poppy | daffodil |
| House   | farmhouse | gothic-revival | modern          | cape-cod    |

