.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, whist, monopoly
House: cottage, cape-cod, tower, palace
1. the tower house is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
5. the person playing billiard is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Game      | whist | billiard  | domino | monopoly |
| House   | cottage  | tower | palace           | cape-cod   |

