.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, august, may
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, van, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | january | april | may | august  |
| Transport           | trike | subway      | van | roller |

