.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, rock-climbing, baking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, oliveros, prince, havana
1. the havana-smoker is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the prince-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | gardening  | woodworking | baking   |
| Cigar        | prince | oliveros | havana    | siglo |

