2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the futuristic house is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| House          | modern | craftsman  | futuristic  | gothic-revival |
| Sport   | cricket   | swimming | ice-hockey | soccer   |

