.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, techno, r&b, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, november, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of trance##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | trance     | house | techno |
| Birthday         | december | february | october   | november   |

