2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | december      | august | january | july |
| Game     | snooker | go    | canasta  | billiard |

