4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar      | dunhill   | aristoff | cain   | tiparillo      |
| Food   | orange | eggplant      | papaya | avocado |

