.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, writing, skydiving, gardening
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, turquise, fuchsia, white
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who likes white##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | drawing | skydiving | writing | gardening   |
| Color     | fuchsia  | emerald    | turquise       | white |

 